{"type":"message","id":"2d0aeeab","parentId":"3314e4b8","timestamp":"2026-03-31T18:49:00.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo. **4. Validación de entrega real** ya quedó resuelto.\n\nHecho:\n- documento: **atlas-delivery-validation.md**\n- resumen en Notion\n- commit hecho\n\nRegla central ya dura:\n- coordinado ≠ ejecutado\n- ejecutado ≠ entregado\n- entregado ≠ cerrado\n\nSigo con el **5: estado mínimo por agente**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09d7eb326b5f82d50169cc171a9f548191b2ba98355d607dc1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":212,"output":91,"cacheRead":42240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42543,"cost":{"input":0.0005300000000000001,"output":0.0013650000000000001,"cacheRead":0.01056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012455}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774982937295,"responseId":"resp_09d7eb326b5f82d50169cc171a0d7c819199ddb320db3cf4d5"}}
