{"type":"message","id":"d9a51321","parentId":"561675d7","timestamp":"2026-03-31T19:11:42.380Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3ABA2C625C4C7758AF78\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nYa?"}],"timestamp":1774984302376}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3fbfb50","parentId":"d9a51321","timestamp":"2026-03-31T19:11:46.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09d7eb326b5f82d50169cc1c707a3881918be0d55eb650ff72\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] No todavía.  \nLo correcto es: **yo no se lo “mando” a otro Atlas distinto**, porque **yo ya soy Atlas main** en esta conversación.\n\nO sea: no faltaba reenviarlo, faltaba **ejecutarlo**.\n\nSi quieres, arranco yo mismo con esa tarea sobre Notion:\n- reviso la estructura actual de `Atlas OS - Home`\n- propongo/armo la reorganización operativa\n- y te voy diciendo qué quedó\n\nSi me dices **sí**, paso de una vez a implementación real.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09d7eb326b5f82d50169cc1c7097b88191a363a43ce504d484\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":273,"output":128,"cacheRead":49536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49937,"cost":{"input":0.0006825000000000001,"output":0.00192,"cacheRead":0.012384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0149865}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774984302380,"responseId":"resp_09d7eb326b5f82d50169cc1c6f85c48191ae86b32ef726e286"}}
